in order to run the script follow the instructions bellow:



1- open a terminal

2-go to program.cpp file destination. 

3- g++ -std=c++11 program.cpp

4- ./a.out algorithmType N file



keep in mind the changeable variables are:-
N: Total number of integers to be sorted
algorithmType: Method to be used to sort( ’b’ for Bubblesort or ’m’ for Merge Sort)
file: Input file to be read ("sorted.txt" or "unsorted.txt").
